return {
	["Hello."] = "Witaj.",
	["Hey."] = "Hejka.",
	["You don't have permission to go there. Talk to Overseer Henry of Januszex to be granted an entry."] = "Nie mozesz tu wejsc. Porozmawiaj z Nadzorca Henrykiem aby nadal ci uprawnienia.",
	["I now have my eye on a certain Januszex TM. They have their headquarters far to the east. I would start working on my CV, but first, i need to learn more about the working conditions there. I would like to ask you to go there by {train}. They have a special metro line that stops at their company. When you are there, search for building with 'C' marking outside."] = "Moja matka ostanio truje mi dupe, zebym znalazl sobie wreszcie jakas prace. Mam teraz na oku pewien Januszex. Maja siedzibe bardzo daleko na wschodzie. Skladalbym juz CV, ale najpierw wolalbym poznac tamtejsze warunki pracy. Chcialbym Cie prosic, aby udal sie tam {pociagiem}. Maja specjalna linie metra, ktora zatrzymuje sie pod ich firma. Kiedy dojedziesz na miejsce odszukaj budynek przed ktorym widoczna jest litera 'C'.",
	["Just use the blackboard here to see the schedules of the train."] = "Rozklad jazdy pociagow mozesz sprawdzic na ten czarnej tablicy.",
	["TrainMovingTo"] = "Wyruszyles do: ",
	["Are you new here? This will be your first job: paint the topex hammers. Head to the 'A' building first."] = "To bedzie twoje pierwsze zadanie: Pomalowanie mlotkow Topex TM. Instrukcje znajdziesz przy pasie produkcyjnym w budynku A.",
	["Get to making calculators, you slacker! Go to the 'P' building now."] = "Bierz sie teraz za skladanie kalkulatorow nierobie. Narzedzia pracy znajdziesz w budynku P.",
	["Bring me five hammers painted metallic."] = "Przynies mi piec mlotkow przemalowanych na metalowe.",
	["Non-standard work footwear! For that you will go to the 'S' building and take care of plier work order."] = "Nieprzepisowe obuwie robocze - za kare dzisiaj pojdziesz do budynku S, aby robic cazki.",
	["Should be five calculators! Im still waiting."] = "Mialo byc 5 kalkualtorow. No co jest? Do roboty!",
	["Good job. You just earned your way into the assistant position. You are now granted a permission to use main entrance and exit to the surface."] = "Ok dobra robota. Doceniam twoja prace, dlatego awansuje cie na mlodszego nadzorce areczkow. Zapytaj mnie o swoje {obowiazki}, jezeli jestes gotow. Aha, mozesz od teraz uzywac glownej bramy i wychodzic na powierzchnie.",
	["Im still waiting for those pliers."] = "Wciaz czekam na piec par cazek.",
	["Are you ready to hear about your new {duties}?"] = "Czy jestes gotowy, aby uslyszec o swoich nowych {obowiazkach?}",
	["I have a hunch that the quantity of our soaps and towels is shrinking at above-average rate. Find out more about this, and remember: not every Areczek is a thief, but every thief is Areczek. Bring be about four of each towel and soap."] = "Wydaje mi sie, ze stan recznikow w lazience dla zarzadu sie kurczy, a ilosc mydel zmniejsza sie w nieprzecietnym tempie. Zbadaj te sprawe. I pamietaj: nie kazdy areczek to zlodziej, ale kazdy zlodziej to areczek.",
	["Those goddamn parasites! This company net profit is barely positive, and they are trying to ruin us!"] = "A to nieroby. Ja to dokaldam do tego interesu, a oni jeszcze maja czelnosc podwedzac produkty premium z lazni dla zarzadu.",
	["Actually, bring me just four soaps. I just recalled that there was towel shortage at local walmart when we tried to order them."] = "Chwileczke... w sumie to recznikow nie ma, bo pepco bylo zamkniete w ostatnim tygodniu. W takim razie odzyslak tylko mydla.",
	["A bunch of Areczeks trying to create a worker union. Get rid of their leader, and they will surely yield."] = "Areczki chytrusy proboja utworzyc zwiazek robotniczy. Pozbadz sie ich przywodcy, a na pewno ustapia.",
	["If i recall correctly, their leader won a cozy bed at a poker table. Its located between A and S buildings."] = "Jesli dobrze pamietam, to ich przywodca wygral w pokera przytulne mieszkanie na pietrze miedzy budynkami S i A.",
	["Alright! I YIELD! We will disband our union. Now give me some peace, im sick."] = "Dobra, poddaje sie! Obiecuje rozwiazac nasze zrzeszenie. Teraz dajcie mi spokoj, jestem chory.",
	["Thanks for help. Now i wont have to worry about labour law or some human rights."] = "Dzieki za pomoc. Juz nie bede musial sie martwic o jakis kodeks pracy czy prawa czlowieka.",
	["Good job. Now i have a new mission for you. Take a look at the bookshelf behind me. You can find The Art of Eristics there. You are gonna need it for later mission. Also, i need you to find the two other tomes from this series. I lost one in the caves, near the south gate. Other one i accidentally flushed down the toilet, which caused the northern caves to be flooded. There is underwater lift near the temple; go down to the bottom of the sewer and search there."] = "Mam dla ciebie nowe zadanie. Za mna znajduje sie ksiazka ze zwrotami erystycznymi. Przyda ci sie w nastepnym zadaniu. Znajdz dwie pozostale ksiazki z tej serii. Jedna zgubilem w jaskini pod poludniowa brama, ktora jest teraz zbyt niebezpieczna do wysylania tam nawet Areczkow. Druga spuscilem niechcacy w kiblu, co spowodowalo zalanie jaskini w polnocnym bloku. Przy wejsciu do miejkiej swiatymi jest podwodna winda do wodociagow. Sproboj je przeszukac.",
	["Come back when you are done collecting the books."] = "Wroc, gdy znajdziesz juz wszystkie ksiegi.",
	["Alright, there are all the book you need. Now for the real task: we are hosting a party in the conference room. You can find some of our clients here. Try to convince them to take out a loan for one of our 'pristine' products. The books i had you bring to me were in Swahili, so you wouldnt understand a word. And now: I doth grant unto thee ye might of larcraeft."] = "Ok, przejdzmy teraz do wlasciwiego zadania. W sali konferencyjnej znajduja sie aktualnie nasi klienci. Sproboj ich przekonac do naszych luksusowywch produktow dla konsumentow detalicznych. Te ksiazki byly po kaszubsku, wiec nic bys nie zrozumial. A teraz: ",
	["Every dish cooked in this pot can only make you more slim and fit."] = "Nie przytujesz od zadnej potrawy przyzadzonej w tym garnku.",
	["This smart potion will make you a lovely person."] = "Mikstura milosna. Obowiazkowy przybor kazdego spermiarza.",
	["Assortment of herbs. They cure cancer within 24 hours."] = "Rozne ziola lecznicze. Zwalczaja kazdego raka w maksymalnie 24 godziny.",
	["Loan agreement"] = "Wniosek o kredyt",
	["I'm not superstitous and don't believe in god either. Magical stones and herbs protect me."] = "Nie wierze w boga ani nie jestem przesadna. Magiczne kamienie i ziola mnie chronia.",
	["This is something i needed. Here is my singature."] = "Wlasnie tego potrzebowalem. Oto dokumenty z moim podpisem.",
	["A pot with those properties is what i need. Teacher salary isn't enough even for a single theater ticket. I guess i will have to take out a loan..."] = "Jako nauczycielka, nie ma nawet pieniedzy na teatr. Zeby moc dostac taki garnek, musze wziac kredyt...",
	["Come back when you are done collecting the loan declarations."] = "Wroc, gdy zdobedziesz deklaracje kredytowe od naszych klientow.",
	["Badass, dude - you got all of them to take out a loan for those >products. You are thereby promoted to senior assistant. Now you can access the main cave system on the north."] = "Niezle, wszyscy wzieli kredyt na tak zwane >produkty. To dobry moment, aby przekazac ci, ze zostales awansowany na starszego asystenta. Mozesz teraz dostac sie do glownego systemu jaskin na polnocy.",
	["I have a new mission for you. Do you remember when i mentioned that northern caves are now flooded? Officially, everyone was out when the flooding occured, but acutally it was swarming with miners there. It were rush hours when it happened. Areczek lives dont matter, so noone ever investigated it. Later, cave has been ravaged by hostile water-shaped creatures. One of the dwarfs here had something i need now. Try to find his corpse. You can identify him by his gray Beard."] = "Mam dla ciebie nowe zadanie. Wspominalem, ze polnocna jaskinia zostala zalana. W oficjalnym raporcie podalismy, ze nikogo tam wtedy nie bylo, ale w istocie to byla godzina najwiekszego zapierdolu. Wszyscy, ktorzy utkneli w jaskini pozdychali. Ale chuj z nimi, to tylko areczki. Jeden z nich mial przy sobie cos, co chcialbym teraz odzyskac. Jego cecha szczegolna to szara broda. Aha, w jaskini zalegly sie jakies nieznane istoty, ktore przybieraja ksztlt wody, przez co latwo odniesc wrazenie, ze jaskinia jest bezpieczna. Nic bardziej mylnego.",
	["Grab necklace from that corpse first. Be careful, those monsters are aggressive!"] = "Najpierw zdobadz moj naszyjnik z tego truchla. I oczywicsie uwazaj potwory, ktore tam teraz mieszkaja.",
	["Yeah, this is the one i was looking for."] = "Tak, to wlasnie ten naszyjnik.",
	["What else could you help me with... hmmm. Well, you check can the lava mines for new finds. Reach the top of one of the silos, and check its state by using the special machine. Also some Areczek reported that he found an abandoned cultivator there. Romek, the King of Rats might be interested in it, so give it a try and find it."] = "Z czym jeszcze mozesz tu pomoc... hmm. Sprawdz postepy w magmowej kopalni. Wespnij sie na szczyt ktoregos z silosow i odczytaj stan na maszynie. A tak w ogole to jakis Areczek mowil, ze znalazl porzucony kultywator, ale bal sie go ruszac. Krol szczurow moze byc nim zainteresowany, wiec jak chcesz, to mozesz go poszukac.",
	["Nothing special, as i thought. Now, you have to help me with something. My friend, Fredi, is currently in the north-eastern mines. I need him here, so try to convince him to come. If he wont move, try to find a distilling machine. Its content will make him move. Fredi is very aggressive when drunk, so be careful."] = "No nic. Mam teraz dla ciebie nowe zadanie. Pomoz mi znalezc mojego przyajciela frediego. Zasiedzial sie gdzies w polnocno-wschodnich kopalniach. Jesli nie bedzie chcial sie ruszyc, bedziesz musial znalezc destylator. Jego zawartosc go od razu pobudzi. Uwazaj, po alkoholu jest agresywny.",
	["Give me the booze! Give me the booze!"] = "Daj wodeczke, to pogadamy...",
	["Alrigth, lets go."] = "No to w droge",
	["Come back with Fredi."] = "Wroc tutaj z Fredim",
	["Good job. Give us a moment now."] = "Dobra robota. Daj nam teraz chwile.",
	["Give us a moment."] = "Daj nam jeszcze chwile.",
	["Did you find out what is the password? What is it?"] = "Znalazles co to za haslo? Mozesz mi je podac?",
	["Go and talk with Access-o-bot in eastern part of the castle. Tell him the password, and he will let you in."] = "Poroznawiaj teraz z Access-o-botem. Znajduje sie on we wschodniej czesci zamku. Podaj mu haslo, a cie wpusci.",
	["Yeah, thats it! Go and get rid of our imperator!"] = "Tak, to jest to! Teraz mozesz isc i rozwalic imperatora!",
	["I had a word with my friend Fredi. HE TOLD ME ABOUT HE NEW BMW OUR IMPERATOR IS DRIVING. This goddamn ostentatious thief. You proven yourself reliable. Its time to end him now. To be granted an audience with him, you need to know the password. The password is written on the blackboard, along the cobblestone trail. Not one Areczek is smart enough to figure the workings of the mechanism that reveals it. I cannot leave my position, but you can go and read it. Came back to me when you find it."] = "Fredi powiedzial mi, ze ten ZLODZIEJ imperator jedzi NOWIUTKIM BMW. Udowodniles swoja niezawodnosc. Pora go wykonczyc i odebrac mu wladze nad Januszexepolem. Aby dostac sie do jego komnat, musisz znac specjalne haslo. W poludniowo zachodnich jaskiniach znajdziesz wodospad. Areczki sa zbyt glupie, zeby odnalezc klucz do mechanizmu, ktory odsloni tablice z haslem. Ja musze tu zostac. Wroc do mnie, jak wejdziesz w posiadanie hasla.",
	["BLACKBOARD_DESC"] = function(context)
		local player = context.player
		local password = player:getStorageValue(Storage.SynMarnotrawny.Blackboard)
		return password
	end,
	["No. Im sure its not the password. Try looking behind the waterfall."] = "Nie, to na pewno nie jest dobre haslo. Sproboj poszukac za wodospadem.",
	["Password:"] = "Podaj haslo:",
	["Correct password. Come in."] = "Haslo poprawne. Zapraszamy.",
	["~BZZT~ WRONG PASSWORD. INITIATE: ERADICATION MODE."] = "~BZZT~ ZLE HASLO. INICJACJA TRYBU UNICESTWIENIA.",
	["Alright. For all your effort i present to you this legendary payslip. Dont worry, it works outside our company shop."] = "To nowa era dla naszego kolchozu. Prosze, oto twoja wyplata za to, ze swietnie sie spisales.",
	["A payslip."] = "Pasek z wyplata.",
	["Did you manage to get the payslip?"] = "Udalo ci sie zdobyc pasek z wyplata?",
	["Come back when you have it."] = "Wroc, jak juz go zdobedziesz",
	["Thanks for the info. This is your reward for your good job!"] = "Dzieki za pomoc. Oto twoja nagroda.",
}
